Note: many of these files are available in higher quality in the ETS NIN.com video archive.
See echoingthesound.org for more details, or wait for my next torrent :)

Once upon a time, there was a great NIN fansite called "teamnineinchnails.net", I can prove it: <a href="
http://google.com/search?q=teamnineinchnails.net" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://google.com/search?q=teamnineinchnails.net</a> <a href="
http://web.archive.org/web/20060402222902/http://teamnineinchnails.net/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://web.archive.org/web/20060402222902/http://teamnineinchnails.net/</a>
Unfortunately, it vanished one day.

This is a torrent of the videos that used to be hosted there. 
Some files have been renamed to reflect the name of the link from the site, in the cases where the actual filename sucked.
I'm posting this because i'm sick of seeing these videos put on youtube, and there being nowhere for people to download the original files.
The point of this torrent is to preserve a slice of the ninternet.  Most of these are not the highest quality available, but they are ALL exponentially 
better than any youtube rip.

Fuck youtube.
